{
  "texts": [
    "Our baselines come from the prompting-based GPT-3.5.",
    "We provide GPT-3.5 with three random text-to-SQL samples from new databases.",
    "The input structure is: \"[DDL] + [Comments (optional)] + 3 instances of [Question, SQL] + [Test question]\".",
    "Given the EX metric's strictness, we also employ human evaluation (HE) for SQL query accuracy.",
    "For example, consider the question, \"What is the abstract of 'Optical geometries'?\"."
  ]
}